{"tid":2154490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】房協：使用「武漢肺炎」一詞製造民族間之撕裂及矛盾之嫌","createTime":"2020-08-13T07:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T08:05:08.000Z","uid":128446,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e196859713ebc72f5d9cf62e901274b34f3ed0c2","tid":2154490,"uid":128446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"事源沙田乙泉區議員丘文俊早前喺乙明邨內張貼有關武漢肺炎疫情資訊嘅通告，喺8月12號收到房協出信表示有住戶投訴「武漢肺炎」一詞<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>製造民族間之撕裂及矛盾之嫌</ins></span></span>，建議更改「武漢肺炎」一詞為「2019冠狀病毒病」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWvYHfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWvYHfU.jpg&h=bf012575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>傳送門：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10214479084610684&amp;id=1826784997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10214479084610684%26id%3D1826784997&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=88771aa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10214479084610684&amp;id=1826784997</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隨後啱啱丘議員喺Facebook公開咗回覆房協嘅信函，內容真係好抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n完整公開信傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10214483532921889&amp;id=1826784997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10214483532921889%26id%3D1826784997&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=ef8c0736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10214483532921889&amp;id=1826784997</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>  [...] 到2019年年底，2019冠狀病毒病疫情在武漢暴發，武漢肺炎一詞開始深入民心。而武漢，亦走向國際，走向世界。<br />\n<br />\n　　本人自幼喜讀中國史，對中華之歷史及文化略有經涉。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">請　貴處闡述，「武漢肺炎」一詞如何製造民族間之撕裂及矛盾？我中華武漢，在　貴處眼中或者認知中，是不是特別得卑劣或者為港人所厭惡？否則，　貴處如何會得出「武漢肺炎」一詞令民族間之撕裂的看法？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n　　根據《中華人民共和國憲法》及《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區基本法》的規定、中央人民政府及香港特別行政區政府的一個中國立場，香港是屬中華人民共和國不可分割的部份，武漢、香港乃屬一個中華民族，血濃於水。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">除非　貴處認為香港與武漢屬不同民族？彼此有敵對仇恨？因此本人不明白函中提述「民族間之矛盾」所指為何？<br />\n<br />\n　　本人藉此提醒　貴處，根據《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》，　請　貴處謹言慎行，錯誤描述有可能觸犯該法第三章第一節訂明，分裂國家罪行。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n　　最後，本人奉勸　貴處多做實事，認真處理邨內管理事務為要，例如改善乙明邨街市管理及清潔衛生、鼠患、邨內聚集非法賭博等重要問題。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n　<br />\n丘議員喺Facebook有提及其他區嘅區議員都有話房協其他屋邨都唔俾張貼「武漢肺炎」通告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，房協唔係政府部門都咁奶... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外唔講唔知原來政府官方都有用過「武漢肺炎」一詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a389dd5abe87d7ce8547345c3ea57275fa3b2d67","tid":2154490,"uid":63157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"知道啦武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"cd7cb33f366ee858d521055fa85500ed18b13544","tid":2154490,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e793854d2f811382e120c45b19bb876a81bb3790","tid":2154490,"uid":23672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"咁改做於武漢最先爆發的肺炎囉"},{"pid":"28935b7bb76c1906ebd0bce9a5edb311bbd181a6","tid":2154490,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"回信鬥紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b45acc795db671fc9f0b6c1a745bd9d0574dd4b","tid":2154490,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"好的 中國武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"94a64db9cdc9b00e7b70417112b437ba51021dd4","tid":2154490,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28935b7bb76c1906ebd0bce9a5edb311bbd181a6","tid":2154490,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s